rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0001
rows.name:
You've returned with the Holy Grail and
the third sword in hand, I see.

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0002
rows.name:
Which means that your next port of
call will be your last: the World Tree.

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0003
rows.name: I wish you a safe journey to Eden.

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0004
rows.name:
You'd better be pulling your own
weight, Zeke.

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0005
rows.name:
Yes, thanks for that, father.
I think you've drilled that into me
enough for me to realize.

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0007
rows.name:
If I were a few years younger, I would
have joined you, but it was not to be.
